        <mxCell id="zlTYj0u4ar4xw8pNr_UX-72" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;ii.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Event Information Display: The user must be able to view comprehensive details for a specific event, including the No of Seats (available vs. occupied), a detailed Description, and Metadata (cast, duration, language, ratings).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;iii.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Event Information Display: The user must be able to view comprehensive details for a specific event, including the No of Seats (available vs. occupied), a detailed Description, and Metadata (cast, duration, language, ratings).&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="30" width="1430" x="730" y="11210" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="zlTYj0u4ar4xw8pNr_UX-73" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;Non-Functional Requirements&lt;/font&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="30" width="270" x="730" y="11300" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="zlTYj0u4ar4xw8pNr_UX-74" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="&lt;div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;Target Scale: The system must be designed to support 100 Million Daily Active Users (DAU).&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;High Availability: When users are searching or viewing an event, the system must prioritize being &quot;always online&quot; (High Availability). It is better to show slightly older data than to show an error page.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;High Consistency: When a user is booking a specific ticket, the system must be Highly Consistent. Two people should never be able to book the exact same seat at the exact same time.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="30" width="730" x="700" y="11390" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
